        "text": "This",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " covenant is between all the gathered representatives and the young king, Jehoiada no doubt putting all things into shape. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And he said unto them, Behold, the king's son shall reign",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The ",
        "children": []
